            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0x67954E4F<!--Today is a <b>Waning Crescent Moon</b>, so here's what I can share with you, Kiddo:\n\nI am called the Guardian Tree due to my protective... Wait for it... Nature! I kid, I kid, but I always watch out for those in need, that's why I take care of Alice here! Sims can stop by to rest and refresh themselves, as well as listen to my tales of wisdom. I've been around for an eternity, literally, and through my roots, I absorb the mystical waters of the Baleful Bog and the goings on of the world.\n\nWhatever gossip or speculation you come across, remember I was there to witness it! It's true! <i>No caps!</i> Also, why the heck do youths get the cringe when I use their dialect? I'm cool. I dab. I can t-pose...or <i>tree pose</i>, I should say. Ha! But not everyone is ready for the truth. A kid <i>ghostied</i> me the other day for talking about the conspiracy theory I've got about the true nature of our reality—that we're not really in control of our own actions. I'm afraid I've already said too much...--></T>
